data.description: Step into to your dream home in the hidden waterfront subdivision of Cypress Lake Circle! This stunning presale new construction home by Eastern Carolina Homes LLC is the epitome of luxury and offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic elegance on a large lot. This spacious home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms as well as a half bathroom on the main floor, providing plenty of space for relaxation and privacy. The open concept design is perfect for entertaining, with a gorgeous kitchen featuring stunning granite counters and a large kitchen island that is perfect for food prep and hosting guests. This floor plan features a split floor plan with primary suite on one side and two guest rooms with full bathroom between them on the other side of the home. The main floor also features modern fixtures and beautiful LVP flooring throughout, providing a sleek and stylish look that is easy to maintain. Upstairs, you'll find a bonus room that can be used as a fourth bedroom or a home office, along with an additional full bathroom. This flexible space is perfect for those who need a bit of extra room for guests or hobbies. All of this on over one acre!Don't miss your chance to own this stunning new construction home in one of Washingtons hidden gems!
